FontView
(c) 2006, Alex Roberts <alex AT redprocess DOT com>

Highly experimental testing code for future font handling widget.


BUILDING
========

Requires Gtk+ 2.10+, Cairo, Pango, Freetype2.

To build:
 gcc font-model.c font-view.c main.c -o fv `pkg-config --libs --cflags gtk+-2.0 pango freetype2`

To run:
 ./fv /path/to/a/typeface
 
 
 
See COPYING for license information.
